00:06:04.364 --> 00:06:06.157
e to the C one.

00:06:06.088 --> 00:06:07.590
Now this is just e to some constant,

00:06:08.382 --> 00:06:09.398
so we could just call this,

00:06:09.542 --> 00:06:12.043
let's just call that the constant C.

00:06:12.043 --> 00:06:16.008
So this is all simplified to C e,

00:06:16.716 --> 00:06:20.338
C e to the kt,

00:06:21.275 --> 00:06:24.190
